Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:53.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}一路前行至今
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:55.49,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}并不是什么大不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:01:00.98,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}只是偶尔会犯错会跌倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.98,0:01:02.97,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}盲目去追寻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.97,0:01:05.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}明知在勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:10.73,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}都只为遵守无声的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:13.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}不想当任风摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:14.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}静静流动的云彩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:20.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}将过去曾经发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:22.91,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}想要超越的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:24.74,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}默默地留在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.74,0:01:29.04,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}别灰心 别后悔Yeh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.04,0:01:30.21,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3\c&H4134AB&}on the way to GO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.21,0:01:34.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}这条路有无限可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:38.59,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}脚踏实地比大步迈进更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:39.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3\c&H4134AB&}on the way to GO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:43.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条路上即使是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:47.49,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}只要笑着一定会传达给谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.84,0:00:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是今天早上在信箱里发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在家里也很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈都有事出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到这种情况只能联系警察了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 沙羽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Switch 14岁 春
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(244,401)} {\t(18,\fs2)}{\fad(0,1000)}{\bord1.5\c&HECEAEF&\b5}第二十五话 Switch off
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.78,0:02:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有受到实质上的伤害 警察是不会出动的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你说我们该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能自卫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.86,0:02:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自卫是指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 沙羽一定要和朋友一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 哪怕是细节都好 我们需要掌握那个男人的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能抓住他的话那再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车站前的小胡同里开了一家卖防卫商品的店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去那里买防身用的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 听起来不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫什么点击枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是电击枪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥 你能陪我一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我来保护沙羽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.99,0:03:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得电击枪只能在一瞬间制止对方的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不能造成其昏迷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了 就算拿着那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要真发生了什么事 沙羽你会用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是比起什么都没有要好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 应对跟踪狂的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如用类似报警器之类能发出巨大响声的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报警器还有布娃娃形式的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂在包上也很放心 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有道理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊 Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好建议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是建议而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得又有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}真的吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我根本…无法保护沙羽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们快走吧 老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天还有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Switch 你陪她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 刚刚你都说可以陪我去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正 你和Switch一起去不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙羽她很为难啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:03:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Switch 因为你比我更可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 小肚鸡肠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比我更能胜任此事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 走吧 沙羽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别再这样叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是看错你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏我一直那么信赖你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也深有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩都要出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃午饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我们回来之后再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点急事要办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙羽你想成为谁的新娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 老哥的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊 Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不如就嫁给Switch吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 沙羽那家伙 忘记带手机了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙羽的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为正好走到这附近 所以就过来看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沙羽也不接电话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙羽的话去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找她有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 是有点事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…说不定你也听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于跟踪狂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掌握了些情报 打算告诉她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人叫三上信治
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说中学时候曾用刀子刺伤过同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后 因为考虑到周围的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有声张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用刀…刺伤了别人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…没必要刻意和那种男人发生纠葛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要放任一阵子他自然会罢手的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙羽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥说的店应该是在这一带吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺难找的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 看起来是个很难缠的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我会小心的 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于刚才的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:06:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Switch 看那边 那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是那个转角的那家店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 老哥…什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和弟弟联系上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且算是已经告诫他了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 沙羽和你弟弟在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他们在车站后那条街上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人开开心心地一起去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我擅自误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙羽并没有和你在交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没有 没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说 那两个人在交往中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做过什么被人记恨的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上什么人都有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是 也因为沙羽很受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真会说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 沙羽 你还记得照片上烟花大会那天的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那天我们两个迷路了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙羽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能随便乱跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来找我们的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 这是理所当然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是你们的老哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥其实一点也没变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也依旧是我们的老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以刚才的事情别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是有点担心 我去找那两个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:08:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 三上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 休息日居然都跟家里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想跑 你这跟踪狂！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他该不会带着刀子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是三上信治吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不关你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带着刀子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像误会什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是什么跟踪狂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子 你不是跟踪沙羽了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实有跟在她后面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我只是想对她表白而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请她和我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:10:00.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:00.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是每次放学回家的时候她总是和那家伙在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是没有好时机…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别瞎掰 你中学的时候不是曾把同学刺伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道那件事是从雪野那里听到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你认识她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么认不认识…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾经交往过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学毕业典礼上 雪野向我告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很快就分手了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她平时很文静 是个不错的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是感情上的起伏却很剧烈…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙到底在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分手的时候也让我吃了不少苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断的咆哮 哭泣 完全不听我说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但自从我有了想从她身边逃离的冲动之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就对新生中很有人气的沙羽一见钟情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我想向她告白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 那么我们分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但自从那天以后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论什么时候 雪野都和沙羽在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻碍着我的告白 并且把我当做尾随变态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么刚才她说到的小刀的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是中学二年级时候雪野自己犯下的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 她的感情起伏太激烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许由于我的事情 对沙羽心怀怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那个女人来家的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 好巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实是想来告诉沙羽这件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！ 沙羽 Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 雪野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和男朋友轻轻热热约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不错的休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却是因为你而被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不想让你知道太多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来打算在你什么都不知道的情况下解决一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是全都暴露了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经什么都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何东西 任何东西 任何东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙羽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙羽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Switch！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Switch！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和义…正文…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正文死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和义…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们对平井雪野进行了审问
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她本意似乎是打算刺杀沙羽小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她发现如果伤害一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是伤害她最重要的人更有效…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说雪野把正文错认为是沙羽的男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…你到底在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她本人也说并不打算杀死他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又因为她现在依旧精神有些混乱 并不能很冷静的了解事情的严重性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说 那两个人在交往中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和义！和义！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}和义！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 这不就是我的错吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:15:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为我说了那么一句无聊的话…Switch就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正文就这样死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和义 请你节哀顺便
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 沙羽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 其实她是最应该来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…还没能恢复过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥 你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟本来就很有才能 被这个世界所需要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来应该会成为个出名的大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我很不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Switch这个绰号 我挺喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Switch 不在了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不在这个世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为我的随口一说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪短一点？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少见你这样啊 笛吹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直是这个长度的嘛 难道是想换个心情？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧 或者说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经快想把自己杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和义 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜的镜片换掉了 现在是平光镜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适合我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这么做 正文也不会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你想代替正文？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样太奇怪了 和义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有想成为Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了不失去Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想至少在这个世上留下他的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的我 很奇怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥你打算成为Switch吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这么做了又会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在惩罚自己吗？老哥你就是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊！不要惩罚自己 来责备我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 沙羽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.99,0:17:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有老哥你那样坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚强？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重身体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我们不会再见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢过你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又失去了重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是改变形象吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笛吹视力挺好的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说他弟弟去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才和他搭话 他让我叫他Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个好像是他弟弟的绰号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个我知道 他现在的外表很像他弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这个样子啊 真恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笛吹 完全没有流眼泪 样子也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来兄弟关系就挺好的 果然是受到打击了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上起床 上学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了夜晚 睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又到早上 起床上学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了夜晚 睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.01,0:18:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天睡得好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Switch 你帮我看看电脑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试的结果怎样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本书 看了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情竟然变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}将来有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想跟你说更多的话 Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说的话语 有很多很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从窗口吹来的风令人不快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我关上了窗户
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说 那两个人正在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从此不再开口讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥 哪天我们三个人再一起去看烟花大会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 哪天一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪天…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和义 晚饭我放这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:21:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 我是Switch 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a i u e o 这…这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我打开这扇窗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我伸出救赎之手的人的出现…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.34,0:21:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那之后的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想被埋进土里看星星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(428,386)\fad(400,0)\c&H000000&\3c&HFDFDFD&}笛吹和义     17岁 秋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是Liberty小真的声音！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了多少个真的啊 弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.37,0:23:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到大姐居然是真女神的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.79,0:23:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此 这位百香大人可是在下最得意的弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.61,0:23:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁是你弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.94,0:23:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 算了 这里就让着振藏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让他威风下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.99,0:23:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然大姐这么说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.90,0:23:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 居然无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.76,0:23:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 Bossuo~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.20,0:23:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能见到您真是三生有幸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.79,0:23:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您一定要收我为小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一辈子追随你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.80,0:23:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？突然这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.15,0:23:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你一个人在这里傻笑个啥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.51,0:23:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.54,0:24:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起过来吧 别在这傻坐着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.95,0:24:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Switch你帮我对付下这小子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.73,0:24:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我这个情报通来告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.70,0:24:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括她三围在内的不好意思告诉别人的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.68,0:24:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.13,0:24:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说Switch不许你这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.58,0:24:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.66,0:24:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下也
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.96,0:24:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.59,0:24:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们得意忘形的话小心我要你们好看啊
